name: 円香
text: 各駅なら何本かあるけど\n乗り換えだるいでしょ
trans:
There're a few trains in other stations,
but it's a pain to change trains, no?

name: 雛菜
trans:
Hey～ Madoka-senpai～
Where do we go～?

name: 小糸
trans: E-Even though there's nothing to eat...!

name: 透
text: にゃあにゃあ\n言ってる

name: 小糸
text: あ、本当だ……\nたくさんいるね！
trans:
Ah, you're right...
A whole lot of them!

name: 透
trans: I wonder if there are fishes too.

name: 小糸
text: いるんじゃないかな……\nあっちにあるの漁船だよね
trans:
There should be...
There's a fishing boat over there.

name: 円香
text: 漁船があるなら、\n食堂もありそうなのに
trans:
If there are fishing boats,
there should also be diners.

name: 円香
text: 正確にはあるけど遠い
trans: To be precise, there is one far away.

name: 雛菜
trans: Hinana's okay with walking you know～?

name: 円香
text: 口コミもないし、営業時間も書いてない\nリスクが大きい
trans:
No reviews were given nor opening hours stated.
We'll be taking quite the risk going.

name: 円香
trans: Let's just skip a meal today.

name: 雛菜
text: 夜に１日分食べないとだね～
trans: Then fill our belly up all at once during dinner～

name: 円香
trans:
For the train?
Shall we head back?

name: 雛菜
text: 円香先輩～\nぬい、忘れてる～

name: 円香
trans: I don't have anywhere to display it.

name: 小糸
text: て、手作りだって言ってたよ！

name: 小糸
text: 手作りのプレゼント、だって……！
trans: A present made by a fan...!

name: 小糸
text: 直接は会ってないけど……\nスタッフさんに渡してくれたみたい
trans:
Although we never met directly...
They were passed to a staff.

name: 小糸
text: あ、あと……\n『一緒に並べて置いてほしい』って言ってたって
trans:
A-Also...
They wanted us to "line them up together".

name: 円香
text: ……各人で持ち帰ったらバラバラになるけど
trans:
...But they'd be separated if we each bring one 
home.

name: 雛菜
text: あ～\nじゃあ、透先輩のところに置く～？
trans:
Ah～
Then should we just display them at Toru-senpai's
place?

name: 雛菜
trans: Or should we display them in the office～?

name: 小糸
text: お、置く場所もらえるかな……？
trans: W-Will they give us a space to put them though...?

name: 小糸
text: 乗るはずの急行……だったよね……？
trans: the express train we should have... taken...?
